WEBVTT

00:01.882 --> 00:06.935
The following story is fictional and
does not depict
any actual person or event.

00:07.268 --> 00:09.886
In New York City's war on crime,

00:09.886 --> 00:12.882
the worst criminal offenders
are pursued by the detectives

00:12.882 --> 00:14.805
of the Major Case Squad.

00:14.805 --> 00:17.095
These are their stories.

00:18.486 --> 00:23.114
Saints do not move,
though grant for prayer's sake.

00:23.114 --> 00:26.813
Then move not while
my prayer's effect I take.

00:28.307 --> 00:29.753
Uh, time.

00:30.700 --> 00:32.738
Problem, Romeo?

00:32.990 --> 00:35.304
It's like kissing my grandmother.
I can't.

00:35.304 --> 00:37.617
Try acting.

00:39.151 --> 00:40.515
Let's continue.

00:44.873 --> 00:48.706
Thus from my lips,
by thine my sin is purged.

00:48.706 --> 00:52.994
Then have my lips the sin
that they have took?

00:52.994 --> 00:56.198
Sin from my lips?
O trespass sweetly urged.

00:56.198 --> 00:58.669
Give me back my sin again.

01:01.932 --> 01:03.940
Good choice, Marion.

01:03.940 --> 01:07.889
A round of applause
for our brilliant Juliet.

